      <title>与 Apollo 和 KKR 挂钩的保险公司在 New Twist 中直接购买抵押贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/insurers-tied-to-apollo-kkr-buy-mortgages-outright-in-new-twist</link>
